<title>USA: Aquarion names George Edwards Jr chairman.</title>
<headline>Aquarion names George Edwards Jr chairman.</headline>
<dateline>BRIDGEPORT, Conn. 1996-09-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>Aquarion Co, an environmental testing company, said Monday that it has named George Ewdwards Jr. chairman of the board to succeed Jack McGregor, who will remain a director.</p>
<p>The company said McGregor intends to focus on his development and investment firm, Bridgeport Waterfront Investors, and to build a related law practice with the Bridgeport firm of Cohen &amp; Wolfe.</p>
<p>Edwards, who has been a director at Aquarion since 1988, assumes his new position October 1, the company said.</p>
<p>-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610.</p>
